---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';

import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_KEYWORDS } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} keywords={SITE_KEYWORDS} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
			<article class="article-landing">
				<h1>Fully automated, AI powered bookmarks.</h1>
				<p class="intro">Mindi categorizes all your bookmarks for you, so you don’t have to.</p>
				<a href="https://app.mindi.ai/signup" class="button button-primary button-large" target="_blank">Get Mindi<div class="button-border"></div></a>
				<img src="/landing/hero.png" alt="Mindi dashboard">

				<ul class="flex">
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/icons/mouse.svg" alt="Mouse icon">Save with a tap</h3>
						<p>One click, and it's done.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/icons/tap.svg" alt="Tap icon">Mindi tags it for you</h3>
						<p>Manual organizing? So yesterday.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/icons/search.svg" alt="Search icon">Instantly find it later</h3>
						<p>Lost bookmarks? Never again.</p>
					</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Save with just a tap.</h2>
				<p>Any site, article, video, image, tweet, or text - one tap and you're set. After saving, carry on with your day, as usual.</p>
				
				<video class="feature__video" width="100%" autoplay="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="">
          <source type="video/mp4" src="/landing/click.mp4">
        </video>

				<h2><img src="/icons/stars.svg" alt="" width="26">Mindi's fun club</h2>
				<div>
				<ul class="testimonials">
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/testimonials/tim.png" alt="">Tim Bao</h3>
						<p>The best extension I've ever used! Makes it super easy to save bookmarks, favorite quotes, and images. A real time saver!</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/testimonials/dajana.png" alt="">Dajana Inkic</h3>
						<p>I love this app! The extension is easy to use and easy to reach. Having everything organized and in one place is great.</p>
					</li>
				</ul>

				<ul class="testimonials">
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/testimonials/sabrina.png" alt="">Sabrina Arcella</h3>
						<p>
              Well done! The design and the experience are great! Dead simple to use, solves the problem and just what I needed to get rid of the bookmarks mess.
            </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/testimonials/max.png" alt="">Max Blum</h3>
						<p>
              Mindi's auto-generated tag system is fantastic. It makes filtering your bookmarks so easy. My inner UX Designer is thrilled!
            </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3><img src="/testimonials/sijo.png" alt="">Sijo Vadajeettil</h3>
						<p>
              Mindi allows me to let my ideas flow and organize all my resources in one place. It helps me focus on what matters, without wasting time on organizing.
            </p>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

				<h2>Find things in a flash.</h2>
				<p>Search, filter, and voilà! Instant results with deep search magic.</p>
				
				<video class="feature__video" width="100%" autoplay="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="">
          <source type="video/mp4" src="/landing/find.mp4">
        </video>

				<h2>Save images.</h2>
				<p>Right-click to add browser images to Mindi. Our AI analyzes, recognizes, and tags for you.</p>
				
				<video class="feature__video" width="100%" autoplay="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="">
          <source type="video/mp4" src="/landing/images.mp4">
        </video>

				<h2>Highlighted text.</h2>
				<p>Select any text, and Mindi's AI generates meaningful tags for easy finding later.</p>
				
				<video class="feature__video" width="100%" autoplay="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="">
          <source type="video/mp4" src="/landing/highlight.mp4">
        </video>

				<h2>Share your bookmarks with ease.</h2>
				<p>Effortlessly send bookmark collections to friends or followers, spreading knowledge and inspiration.</p>
				
				<video class="feature__video" width="100%" autoplay="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="">
          <source type="video/mp4" src="/landing/share.mp4">
        </video>

				<a href="https://app.mindi.ai/signup" class="button button-primary button-large" target="_blank">Get Mindi <div class="button-border"></div></a>

				<h2>Privacy and our promise</h2>
				<ul class="flex">
					<li>
						<h3>Totally private.</h3>
						<p>We value privacy like you do. No selling data to third parties. Mindi's your safe place.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Your data, your business. </h3>
						<p>We use product interaction data to improve Mindi, but we analyze collectively, not individually.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Ad-free zone.</h3>
						<p>Our revenue model relies on subscriptions and freemium, not ads.</p>
					</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Safe and secure</h2>

				<p class="small">Mindi's powered by Google Cloud Platform, ensuring top-notch security from our small, independent team.</p>
				<p class="small">Rest easy with the latest industry standards for data security in transit and at rest.</p>
				<p class="small">SSL all the way, 100% cloud-based architecture.</p>
			</article>
			<Footer />
		</div>		
	</body>
</html>

<style lang="scss">
	.article-landing {
		padding-top: 2rem;
		gap: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;

		h1 {
			text-align: center;
			max-width: 800px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			font-size: 5rem;
			line-height: 1.1;

			@media (max-width: 1020px) {
				font-size: 3rem; 
			}
		}

		h2 {
			img {
				display: inline-block;
				opacity: 0.5;
			}
		}

		.intro {
			text-align: center;
			opacity: 0.8;
			margin: 0 auto;
			max-width: 400px;
		}

		a.button {
			align-self: center;
		}

		h1, h2, h3 {
			margin-bottom: 0;
		}

		p {
			margin-bottom: 0;
			max-width: 760px;

			&.small {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
			}
		}

		ul {
			padding-left: 0;

			li {
				padding-left: 0;
				list-style-type: none;
			}
		}

		img, video {
			border-radius: 6px;
		}

		.flex {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between;
			gap: 30px;

			@media (max-width: 760px) {
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0;
			}

			h3, p {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
			}

			h3 {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;

				img {
					display: inline-block;
					margin: 0 10px 0 0;
				}
			}
		}

		.testimonials {
			display: flex;
			gap: 11px;
			margin-bottom: 3px;

			@media (max-width: 760px) {
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0;
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			li {
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
				padding: 20px;
				border-radius: 6px;

				h3 {
					display: flex;
					align-items: center;
					gap: 10px;
					margin-top: 0;
					margin-bottom: 1rem;
					font-size: 1rem;
					font-weight: 500;

					img {
						width: 30px;
						height: 30px;
						border-radius: 50%;
						margin: 0;
					}
				}

				p {
					font-size: 1rem;
					line-height: 1.5;
				}
			}
		}
	}
</style>